taylor2007 <http://www.airs.com/blog/archives/38>

  This is a conversion of the essays written by Ian Lance Taylor on the topic
  of linkers.  The entire collection is indexed here:

    <http://lwn.net/Articles/276782/>

  There is also a recipe using Calibre available for building other ebooks:

    <https://github.com/cataliniacob/calibre-recipes/blob/master/ian-taylor-linker.recipe>

REQUIRES

  Fonts

    * Libertine Linux O <http://www.linuxlibertine.org>
    * Inconsolatazi4 <https://www.ctan.org/tex-archive/fonts/inconsolata/opentype>

  Tools

    * xelatex
    * latexmk
    * make

  Latex packages

    * fontspec
    * hyperref
    * listings
    * xcolor
    * tocloft

BUILDING

  Run make
